<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/93000812/2025-26/evaluation> a ns1:EvaluationSystem ;
    ns1:evaluationDescription """The final grade in the progresive evaluation consists of the marks obtained by simulation reports, quality of the technical document and the presentation of that document:
Final grade = 60% Presentation and quality of the technical document + 40% Exam (alternative opotion instead of simulation reports)
Document preparation an presentation quality minimum level is 5 points.
Extraordinary call
The estraordinary call will consist both in a written exam and the preparation and presentation of a techical document similar to the ordinary call
The written exam is mandatory and its minimum level is 4 points over 10."""@es ;
    ns1:hasEvaluationTrial <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/93000812/2025-26/evaluation/trial1>,
